\c 18
\s UDavida uthandwa nguJonathani, uzondwa nguSawuli
\p
\v 1 Kwasekusithi eseqedile ukukhuluma loSawuli, umphefumulo kaJonathani wabotshelwa emphefumulweni kaDavida\x + Gen. 44.30.\x*; uJonathani wasemthanda njengomphefumulo wakhe\x + 18.3. 19.2. 20.17. 2 Sam. 1.26. Dute. 13.6.\x*.
\v 2 USawuli wasemthatha ngalolosuku, kaze amvumela ukubuyela endlini kayise\x + 17.15.\x*.
\v 3 UJonathani loDavida basebesenza isivumelwano ngoba wamthanda njengomphefumulo wakhe.
\v 4 UJonathani wasezikhulula ibhatshi ayeligqokile, walinika uDavida, lezembatho zakhe, kuze kube senkembeni yakhe, kuze kube sedandilini lakhe, njalo kuze kube sebhantini lakhe.
\p
\v 5 UDavida wasephuma waya loba ngaphi lapho uSawuli amthuma khona, waziphatha ngenhlakanipho, uSawuli waze wambeka phezu kwamadoda empi. Njalo wayelungile emehlweni abantu bonke njalo lemehlweni ezinceku zikaSawuli.
\p
\v 6 Kwasekusithi ekufikeni kwabo, uDavida esebuye ekubulaleni umFilisti, abesifazana baphuma emizini yonke yakoIsrayeli, behlabela, begida, ukuhlangabeza uSawuli inkosi\x + Eks. 15.20. Hlu. 11.34. Hlu. 21.21.\x* ngezigubhu, ngentokozo, langamachacho\x + Eks. 15.20. Hlu. 11.34. Hlu. 21.21.\x*.
\v 7 Abesifazana basebevum\add ela\add*na bedlala bathi\x + 21.11. Eks. 15.21.Nani 21.17.\x*: USawuli utshayile izinkulungwane zakhe\x + 21.11. 29.5.\x*, kodwa uDavida izinkulungwane zakhe ezingamatshumi.
\v 8 USawuli wasethukuthela kakhulu, lalelolizwi lalilibi emehlweni akhe, wathi: Banike uDavida izinkulungwane ezingamatshumi, kodwa mina banginika izinkulungwane; usesalelwe ngumbuso kuphela\x + 15.28.\x*.
\v 9 USawuli wasemqaphela uDavida kusukela kulolosuku kusiya phambili.
\p
\v 10 Kwasekusithi kusisa umoya omubi ovela kuNkulunkulu wafika ngamandla phezu kukaSawuli\x + 16.14. Hlu. 9.23.\x*, waprofetha phakathi kwendlu\x + 19.24. 1 Kho. 18.29. Seb. 16.16.\x*; uDavida wasetshaya ichacho ngesandla sakhe njengensuku ngensuku\x + 16.16.\x*; njalo kwakulomkhonto esandleni sikaSawuli\x + 19.9.\x*.
\v 11 USawuli wasewuphosa umkhonto wathi: Ngizammbandakanya uDavida ngitsho emdulini\x + 20.33. 19.10.\x*. Kodwa uDavida wavika kabili esuka phambi kwakhe.
\p
\v 12 USawuli wayemesaba-ke uDavida\x + 18.29,15.\x* ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* yayilaye\x + 16.18.\x*, kodwa yayisisukile kuSawuli\x + 16.14. 28.15.\x*.
\v 13 Ngakho uSawuli wasemsusa kuye, wambeka waba yinduna yakhe yabayizinkulungwane; njalo wayephuma engena phambi kwabantu\x + 18.16. Nani 27.17. 2 Sam. 5.2.\x*.
\v 14 UDavida waseziphatha ngenhlakanipho endleleni zakhe zonke, leN\nd kosi\nd* yayilaye\x + 18.12.\x*.
\v 15 Lapho uSawuli ebona ukuthi waziphatha ngenhlakanipho enkulu, wamesaba.
\v 16 Kodwa uIsrayeli wonke loJuda bamthanda uDavida, ngoba wayephuma engena phambi kwabo\x + 18.5.\x*.
\p
\v 17 USawuli wasesithi kuDavida: Khangela, indodakazi yami endala uMerabi\x + 14.49.\x*, ngizakunika yona ibe ngumka\add kho\x + 14.49.\x*\add*; kuphela bana liqhawe kimi, ulwe izimpi zeN\nd kosi\x + 25.28. 17.47.\x*\nd*. Ngoba uSawuli wathi: Isandla sami kasingabi phezu kwakhe, kodwa isandla samaFilisti kasibe phezu kwakhe\x + 18.21,25.\x*.
\v 18 Kodwa uDavida wathi kuSawuli: Ngingubani mina? Lempilo yami iyini, \add l\add*osendo lukababa koIsrayeli, ukuthi ngibe ngumkhwenyana wenkosi\x + 18.23. 2 Sam. 7.18.\x*?
\v 19 Kodwa kwathi ngesikhathi uMerabi indodakazi kaSawuli ayezanikwa ngaso uDavida, wayesenikwe uAdriyeli\x + 2 Sam. 21.8.\x* umMehola ukuba ngumka\add khe\x + Hlu. 7.22.\x*\add*.
\v 20 UMikhali indodakazi kaSawuli wamthanda-ke uDavida; basebemtshela uSawuli, lalolodaba lwaluqondile emehlweni akhe\x + 18.28. 14.49.\x*.
\v 21 USawuli wasesithi: Ngizamnika yena ukuze abe ngumjibila kuye\x + Eks. 10.7.\x*, lokuze isandla samaFilisti simelane laye\x + 18.17.\x*. Ngakho uSawuli wathi kuDavida: Ngokwesibili uzakuba ngumkhwenyana wami lamuhla\x + 18.26.\x*.
\p
\v 22 USawuli waselaya inceku zakhe \add wathi\add*: Khulumani loDavida ngensitha lithi: Khangela, inkosi iyathokoza ngawe, lazo zonke inceku zayo ziyakuthanda; ngakho-ke woba ngumkhwenyana wenkosi.
\v 23 Izinceku zikaSawuli zasezikhuluma lawomazwi endlebeni zikaDavida. UDavida wasesithi: Kuyinto elula yini emehlweni enu ukuba ngumkhwenyana wenkosi, lokhu mina ngingumuntu ongumyanga lodelelekayo\x + Nani 16.9.\x*?
\v 24 Lenceku zikaSawuli zamtshela zisithi: UDavida wakhuluma ngalindlela.
\v 25 USawuli wasesithi: Lizakutsho njalo kuDavida \add lithi\add*: Inkosi kayiloyisi lobolo, kodwa amajwabu aphambili alikhulu amaFilisti\x + Gen. 34.12.\x*, ukuze kuphindiselwe ezitheni zenkosi\x + 14.24.\x*. Kodwa uSawuli wacabanga ukwenza uDavida awe ngesandla samaFilisti\x + 18.17.\x*.
\v 26 Lapho inceku zakhe zimtshela uDavida lawomazwi, udaba lwalulungile emehlweni kaDavida ukuthi abe ngumkhwenyana wenkosi\x + 18.20.\x*. Kodwa insuku zazingakagcwaliseki\x + 18.21.\x*.
\v 27 Ngakho uDavida wasukuma wahamba, yena labantu bakhe, basebetshaya phakathi kwamaFilisti amadoda angamakhulu amabili\x + 18.13.\x*; uDavida waseletha amajwabu awo aphambili, wawasa enkosini ephelele ukuze abe ngumkhwenyana wenkosi. USawuli wasemnika uMikhali indodakazi yakhe ukuthi abe ngumka\add khe\x + 2 Sam. 3.14.\x*\add*.
\p
\v 28 USawuli wasebona wazi ukuthi iN\nd kosi\nd* iloDavida, loMikhali indodakazi yakhe yamthanda\x + 18.12.\x*.
\v 29 Njalo uSawuli waya lokhu emesaba kakhulu uDavida\x + 2 Sam. 3.14.\x*; njalo uSawuli waba yisitha sikaDavida zonke izinsuku\x + 2 Kho. 13.3.\x*.
\v 30 Iziphathamandla zamaFilisti zaseziphuma\x + 19.8. 2 Sam. 11.1.\x*; kwasekusithi seziphumile uDavida waziphatha ngenhlakanipho okwedlula zonke izinceku zikaSawuli, laze laduma kakhulu ibizo lakhe\x + 18.5.\x*.
